comes alive.

48
00:02:20,975 --> 00:02:23,141
It exists not on the page, but in our
minds, and

49
00:02:23,141 --> 00:02:25,680
the same is true for mathematics.

50
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,560
Mathematics is a performance.

51
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,630
It's a living act.

52
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:31,810
It's a way of interpreting the world.

53
00:02:31,810 --> 00:02:34,848
