playing the music.

56
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:44,371
Student's wouldn't, wouldn't continue with
the subject because they wouldn't ever

57
00:02:44,371 --> 00:02:46,470
experience what music is.

58
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:51,390
